  "texts": [
    "In these two documents, the positions of all chemical structures were manually annotated.",
    "In each section, 50 images (if available) were randomly selected and their molecular structures were precisely annotated.",
    "In total, this test set was created by manually annotating the position of 1822 molecule images in 235 pages, as well as 141 molecular graphs (MOL files).",
    "Table 6 shows the percentage of correctly retrieved molecules from different patent sections in different chemical-structures databases.",
